"__typename":"PhotoInfo","id":"484243789","highResUrl":"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/a/b/0/d/highres_484243789.jpeg","baseUrl":"https://secure-content.meetupstatic.com/images/classic-events/"},"PhotoInfo:320914479":{"__typename":"PhotoInfo","id":"320914479","highResUrl":"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/8/6/a/f/highres_320914479.jpeg"},"ProNetwork:1121475507299876864":{"__typename":"ProNetwork","id":"1121475507299876864","urlname":"global-aws-user-group-community","name":"Global AWS User Group Community","logo":{"__ref":"PhotoInfo:320914479"},"groups":{"__typename":"ProNetworkGroupsConnection","totalCount":392}},"Member:267776499":{"__typename":"Member","id":"267776499","name":"Gary Wib","isSuperOrganizer":false},"Member:25013682":{"__typename":"Member","id":"25013682","name":"Daniel Drentin","isSuperOrganizer":false},"Member:31642322":{"__typename":"Member","id":"31642322","name":"dale orders","isSuperOrganizer":false,"memberPhoto":{"__ref":"PhotoInfo:297804311"}},"Member:413240193":{"__typename":"Member","id":"413240193","name":"Alp Tuna","isSuperOrganizer":false,"memberPhoto":{"__ref":"PhotoInfo:325792442"}},"Group:26952502":{"__typename":"Group","id":"26952502","name":"Melbourne AWS Programming and Tools Meetup","timezone":"Australia/Melbourne","keyGroupPhoto":{"__ref":"PhotoInfo:484243789"},"urlname":"Melbourne-AWS-Programming-and-Tools-Meetup","isPrivate":false,"organizer":{"__ref":"Member:5467684"},"stats":{"__typename":"GroupStats","memberCounts":{"__typename":"GroupMemberCounts","all":5901,"leadership":5,"pending":0},"eventRatings":{"__typename":"GroupStatsEventRatings","average":4.69,"total":865}},"lat":-37.81,"lon":144.96,"joinMode":"OPEN","status":"PAID","city":"Melbourne","state":"","country":"au","proNetwork":{"__ref":"ProNetwork:1121475507299876864"},"isPrimaryOrganizer":false,"events({\"filter\":{\"status\":[\"DRAFT\"]},\"first\":1})":{"__typename":"GroupEventConnection","totalCount":1},"needsQuestions":null,"needsPhoto":null,"questions":[],"memberDuesSettingsUrl":"https://www.meetup.com/dues/melbourne-aws-programming-and-tools-meetup/start/","duesSettings":null,"calendarFeeds":null,"welcomeBlurb":"Thanks for joining our group\n\nPlease bring your experience and passion and share with everyone else.\n\nPlease be aware that we have zero tolerance for inappropriate behavior. Please help us to make this meetup a safe place for everyone. For more details you can find our Code of Conduct here https://www.meetup.com/Melbourne-AWS-Programming-and-Tools-Meetup/pages/28959544/Code_Of_Conduct/\n\nOnce again, meetup organizers welcome you to the group.","organizerStartTime":null,"memberships:{\"filter\":{\"status\":\"LEADER\"}}":{"__typename":"GroupMemberConnection","edges":[{"__typename":"GroupMemberEdge","node":{"__ref":"Member:5467684"}},{"__typename":"GroupMemberEdge","node":{"__ref":"Member:267776499"}},{"__typename":"GroupMemberEdge","node":{"__ref":"Member:25013682"}},{"__typename":"GroupMemberEdge","node":{"__ref":"Member:31642322"}},{"__typename":"GroupMemberEdge","node":{"__ref":"Member:413240193"}}]},"description":"\u003cp\u003eWe organise \u003cstrong\u003ehands on workshops\u003c/strong\u003e of AWS services in our meetups. We concentrate on serverless development. Main areas of interest are Mobile development/engagement as well as IoT (Internet of Things) platforms\u0026nbsp;and analytics.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eBlog page:\u0026nbsp;\u003ca href=\"https://blog.programming-tools-meetup.cloud/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ehttps://blog.programming-tools-meetup.cloud/\u003c/a\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eGithub repo:\u0026nbsp;\u003ca href=\"https://github.com/oz-cloudtools-meetup/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ehttps://github.com/oz-cloudtools-meetup/\u003c/a\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSlack channel sign up:\u0026nbsp;\u003ca href=\"https://join.slack.com/t/aws-programming-tools/shared_invite/zt-byo92q7b-KFGE13v0o~Uq9qwqny_lNA\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ehttps://join.slack.com/t/aws-programming-tools/shared_invite/zt-byo92q7b-KFGE13v0o~Uq9qwqny_lNA\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAs of Dec 2017 Computing services this group is interested in are as follows:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCompute:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eLambda, Batch, Step\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDatabase:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eRDS, DynamoDB, ElastiCache, Amazon Redshift, Aurora,\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMachine Learning:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eAmazon SageMaker, Amazon Comprehend, AWS DeepLens, Amazon Lex, Machine Learning, Amazon Polly, Rekognition, Amazon Transcribe, Amazon Translate\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAnalytics:\u003c/strong\u003e\u0026nbsp;Glue, CloudSearch, Elasticsearch Service, Kinesis, QuickSight, Athena\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMobile Services:\u003c/strong\u003e\u0026nbsp;Mobile Hub, Mobile Analytics\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eApplication Integration: \u003c/strong\u003eAmazon MQ, Simple Notification Service,\u0026nbsp;Simple Queue Service,\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCustomer Engagement:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eAmazon Connect, Pinpoint\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eInternet of Things:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eAWS IoT,\u0026nbsp;IoT Device Management,\u0026nbsp;Amazon FreeRTOS,\u0026nbsp;AWS Greengrass\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eLooking forward to meeting all passionate developers.\u003c/p\u003e","video":null,"featuredEvent":null,"events({\"filter\":{\"status\":[\"ACTIVE\"]},\"first\":4,\"sort\":\"ASC\"})":{"__typename":"GroupEventConnection","totalCount":1,"edges":[{"__typename":"EventEdge","node":{"__ref":"Event:315298544"}}]},"events({\"filter\":{\"status\":[\"PAST\"]},\"first\":4,\"sort\":\"DESC\"})":{"__typename":"GroupEventConnection","totalCount":88,"